verbose_text: Further, some studies suggested that activation of dopamine receptors (type 1 and type 2) could increase production of IL-6 and IL-17.18, 19 These cytokines are strongly associated with the development of ADs, including RA, SLE, and SS.20, 21, 22, 23 Nevertheless, an Iranian pilot randomized double-blind clinical trial assessed the effect of cabergoline in RA patients, showing improvement in tender and swollen joint count, and patients pain assessment.
